name: angular-diff-match-patch
body:
angular-diff-match-patch
========================

This library is simply a wrapper around [google-diff-match-patch](https://code.google.com/p/google-diff-match-patch/).

More to come, but see [this demo](http://run.plnkr.co/plunks/6FIj2oiOPFty9VkWVZEF/) for reference!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
